title: Miranda_Lambert-Crazy_Ex-Girlfriend-2007
description:
Big talk from a small-town Texas girl, but Lambert&#039;s got
 the goods to back it up. The old-school passion and 
power of her nearly platinum-selling 2005 debut KEROSENE
took it to the top of both the country charts and the 
critics&#039; polls. Now the two-time CMA Horizon Award 
nominee returns with Crazy Ex-Girlfriend, on which she
raises the stakes both musically and emotionally.

"My songs talk about real things," says Miranda Lambert.
"Things that I&#039;ve been through or I&#039;ve witnessed through 
my friends and family - even my parents&#039; private
investigation business. If I feel it, I can sing it and
make anyone believe it.


                Miranda Lambert - Crazy Ex-Girlfriend
